Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快對我開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,成瀨她在哪裡?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成瀨!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:59.95,title,Hong Shao,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,897)\fade(255,0,225,0,1001,4921,5460)}遙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,成瀨 妳聽得見嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,成瀨荊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快回答!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:01:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先把她轉過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,出血很嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,砲彈的碎片刺進身體裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在沒有心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,深作葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.48,Default,AED,0,0,0,,你去裝甲車後面拿AED過來!
